name: Journals | A5
description:
[Currently available at markets and wholesale only]

A place to capture your life, dreams and creativity!

For those who enjoy putting pen to paper and recording the details of life and experience, our journals are the perfect home for reflection, observation and inspiration.  

The bright white recycled pages inside are lined on one side and plain on the reverse, providing an ideal home for diary entries, life plans, sketches and whimsy.  

The soft front cover is based on original photographic artwork and complemented by a sturdy black hardback. Wirebound on the left. 

Handmade in small batches in our Melbourne workshop.
125 pages - lined, plain on reverse
White 100% recycled paper
220 x 115 mm
Covers based on images in the Print Collection. See tab on main website

description:

name: Everyday Notebooks | A6
description:
[Currently available at markets and wholesale only]

Useable art in your pocket!

This handy notebook is the perfect size for using on the go, fitting easily into your pocket or handbag. Filled with unlined white recycled paper, it is crisp and bright and perfect for both notes and sketches.

The vibrant glossy photographic cover is complemented by the sturdy matte black hardback. Wirebound on the left, it is both compact and stylish for everyday use.

Handmade in small batches in our Melbourne workshop.
125 pages - plain, white recycled paper
140 x 115 mm

name: Card Sets | Fridge Magnet
description:
[Currently available at markets and wholesale only]

Our signature Greeting Cards are designed to be useable artpieces. The miniature photo print is presented on a stylish black card body echoing our full size framed art prints. 

The image is mounted using classic photo corners, reminiscent of vintage photo albums. And when the card has been enjoyed, the photograph can be detached for reuse as a fridge magnet.

Handmade in small batches in our Melbourne workshop.
Original design
Black textured card
100% unbleached recycled paper inlay page and envelope
